This client for [Twoffein](http://twoffein.com/)'s [API](http://twoffein.com/api-faq/).

## Installation

Add this line to your application's Gemfile:

    gem 'twoffein-client'

And then execute:

    $ bundle

Or install it yourself as:

    $ gem install twoffein-client

